name: CyberLand: An Encrypted Tale
description:
CyberLand: An Encrypted Tale is a platformer type game made by the team OakVale Studios. This main goal of the game is to find an exit to each of the 6 levels and finish the game.

Controls 

Keyboard Move - ARROW KEYS
Jump - Z
